---
title: Quick Spiced Pork & Romesco Sauce with Spinach Rice & Garlicky Green Beans
description: This meal is all about the little differences – the homely seasoning spicing up the pork, the easily-cooked bed of fluffy rice and
the smokey, Spanish-inspired romesco sauce that's bound to be your new favourite accompaniment.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
